  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p736166/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201506/e83f4b8c9eb64dc2ae9f6f9695fde058.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tSony Pictures and Marvel Studios announced Tuesday that Tom Holland will play the title role in the next film about the web-slinger.索尼影业和漫威影业公司于周二宣布，汤姆&middot;霍兰德将担纲主演新蜘蛛侠。</p>\n<p>\n\tThe hero&rsquo;s next adventure won&rsquo;t <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/swing\" target=\"_blank\">swing</a> into theaters until 2017, which gives us plenty of time to study up on the actor playing the next <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/incarnation\" target=\"_blank\">incarnation</a> of Peter Parker. Here are five things to know about him:新蜘蛛侠将在2017年才回归影院，因此我们还有很多时间来好好研究即将饰演彼得&middot;帕克的这只小鲜肉。以下是关于他我们需要了解的5件事：</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>1. He&rsquo;s got moves他可是很能跳的哦~</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tThe British-born Holland got his big break when he was <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/spotted\" target=\"_blank\">spotted</a> by a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/choreographer\" target=\"_blank\">choreographer</a> while performing with his dance school at a 2006 festival. Eight auditions and two years of training later, he made his <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/debut\" target=\"_blank\">debut</a> in Billy Elliot the Musical as Michael, Billy&rsquo;s best friend, before later moving into the main role.这只英国小鲜肉霍兰德初次崭露头角呢是在06年参加舞蹈学校表演的时候被一个编舞发掘的。先后参加过8次海选，随后经过两年的训练，首次出演音乐剧《跳出我天地》，饰演迈克尔，即比利的好朋友。之后获得出演主要角色的机会。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>2. He&rsquo;s already done The Impossible&hellip;他出演了《海啸奇迹》</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tAfter finishing his run in Billy Elliot the Musical in 2010, Holland landed his first film role in The Impossible, about a family caught in Thailand during the 2004 Indian Ocean <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/tsunami\" target=\"_blank\">tsunami</a>.2010年退出音乐剧《跳出我天地》的表演后，霍兰德获得了出演电影《海啸奇迹》的机会。《海啸奇迹》讲述的是一个家庭在2004年印度洋海啸中被困泰国的事情。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>3. &hellip;and shared screen time with Thor与雷神锤哥一同出演。</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tHolland has already crossed paths with another Marvel hero. He stars alongside Chris Hemsworth in Ron Howard&rsquo;s upcoming In the Heart of the Sea, out in theaters this December.霍兰德已经和另一位漫威英雄相遇。他与克里斯&middot;海姆斯沃斯一同出演由朗&middot;霍华德执导，即将于今年12月份上映的《海洋深处》。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>4. Locking down Spider-Man wasn&rsquo;t easy能够出演新蜘蛛侠并不容易</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tMarvel and Sony&rsquo;s announcement noted the studios and <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/execs\" target=\"_blank\">execs</a> were wowed by his performances in The Impossible, In the Heart of the Sea and his role on the TV miniseires Wolf Hall, but that wasn&rsquo;t enough &ndash; he also went through &ldquo;a series of complex screen tests&rdquo; to land the part.漫威和索尼表示被霍兰德在《海啸奇迹》、《海洋深处》、以及迷你剧《狼厅》中的演出所惊艳到。但这些还远远不够，为了得到新蜘蛛侠的角色，霍兰德还经历了一系列复杂苦难的试镜。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>5. But he has no trouble with&nbsp;<a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/backflip\" target=\"_blank\">backflips</a>他还会后空翻</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tLast, but certainly not least&hellip;if these <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/stunts\" target=\"_blank\">stunts</a> he posted on Instagram are any indication, he won&rsquo;t have any trouble swinging around as Spidey.最后但同样重要的是，如果霍兰德在Instagram上秀出的惊人表演（后空翻）要暗示点什么的话，那就是这只小蜘蛛的动作戏将会游刃有余，相当精彩。（就让我们拭目以待吧~）</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p736166/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p736166\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p736062/\">初学者：VOA和BBC并不是练听力的好方法</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p735984/\">王俊凯微博转发破四千万 创吉尼斯世界纪录</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p734978/\">一张图告诉你 使用人数最多的23种语言</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p735858/\">万万没想到：自毁人生的n种做法</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p735960/\">世界上有两种人 你是哪一种？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p736032/\">孤独寂寞冷的“备胎”词汇（一）</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p735505/\">低头党的福音：美国校园设玩手机专用人行道</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p734099/\">《英雄联盟》里的英文单词 孙悟空篇</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p736092/\">夏日纯色搭配：教你穿出最美的白色</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p736105/\">牛津词典告诉你 英语里一共有多少单词</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
  "title": "你所不知道新蜘蛛侠Tom Holland的5件事"
